cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM 

The paper proposes a convolutional neural network (ConvNet) based approach for learning local image descriptors, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of a multi-resolution ConvNet for learning keypoint descriptors suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The evaluation of the approach on publicly available datasets suggests a focus on graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM).
